<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Per Christian Berg | Music | Christian Berg</title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-primary">
    <div id="main" class="h-full mx-auto w-full lg:w-10/12 xl:w-8/12">
      {{> header }}
      <div class="relative">
        <img
          src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dvkodtgl9/image/upload/c_scale,q_auto:good,w_1440/v1629986340/perchristianberg.com/music/christian-berg"
          alt="Christian Berg hero image"
          class="h-screen sm:h-fixed object-cover w-full object-center"
          />
        <div class="absolute top-0 bottom-0 left-0 right-0 gradient"></div>
      </div>
      <main class="my-32 flex flex-wrap lg:p-0 p-4">

        <section aria-label="Project and section headline" class="">
          <h1 id="header-title" class="mb-8 xl:text-title1 2xl:text-title2 sm:text-title2 text-project text-white uppercase font-display">christian berg</h1>
          <div class="text-white font-body w-full mb-32">
            Moving in the atmospheric landscapes from ambient to techno. Deeply inspired by nature and stillness.
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 md:gap-32 mb-16 md:mb-32">
          {{#each htmlWebpackPlugin.options.albums }}
            {{#with this}}
              {{> albumv}}
            {{/with}}
          {{/each}}
        </section>

        <section aria-label="Mixes and resources section" class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 md:gap-32 lg:p-0">
          <div class="">
            <h3 class="text-white font-display mb-8 text-lg uppercase">Mixes</h3>
            <!-- <h3 class="mb-4 text-white font-display text-opacity-50 uppercase">Mixes</h3> -->
            <div class="text-white font-body mb-8">Have a listen to a podcast episode I created for Drivhuset Podcast series</div>
            <iframe width="100%" height="300" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" allow="autoplay" src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/587897313&color=%236299a9&auto_play=false&hide_related=false&show_comments=true&show_user=true&show_reposts=false&show_teaser=true&visual=true"></iframe><div style="font-size: 10px; color: #cccccc;line-break: anywhere;word-break: normal;overflow: hidden;white-space: nowrap;text-overflow: ellipsis; font-family: Interstate,Lucida Grande,Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Sans,Garuda,Verdana,Tahoma,sans-serif;font-weight: 100;"><a href="https://soundcloud.com/drivhuset-meraki" title="Drivhuset-Meraki" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;">Drivhuset-Meraki</a> Â· <a href="https://soundcloud.com/drivhuset-meraki/drivhuset-podcast-16-christian-berg-form-formless" title="Drivhuset Podcast #16 Christian Berg - Form, Formless" target="_blank" style="color: #cccccc; text-decoration: none;">Drivhuset Podcast #16 Christian Berg - Form, Formless</a></div>
          </div>
          <div class="">
            <h3 class="text-white font-display mb-8 text-lg uppercase">Resources</h3>
            <div class="text-white font-body w-full lg:w-4/5 mb-8">
              For further information about how and where you can listen, here are some resources to check out if your interested.
            </div>
            <div class="grid gap-6 grid-cols-2 w-full lg:w-4/5">
              <button class="icon-button">
                <a href="https://open.spotify.com/artist/0kHutYBsThHxb4q2aUjn67?si=J7bipZ1aRSenDNEHMigcLg" target="_blank" class="flex justify-center">
                  {{> icons/spotify class="h-6 w-6" }}
                  <span class="ml-2">Spotify</span>
                </a>
              </button>
              <button class="icon-button">
                <a href="https://soundcloud.com/christian_berg1" target="_blank" class="flex justify-center">
                  {{> icons/soundcloud class="h-6 w-6" }}
                  <span class="ml-2">Soundcloud</span>
                </a>
              </button>
              <button class="icon-button">
                <a href="https://stereoscenic.bandcamp.com/album/skogsro" target="_blank" class="flex justify-center">
                  {{> icons/bandcamp class="h-6 w-6" }}
                  <span class="ml-2">Bandcamp</span>
                </a>
              </button>
              <button class="icon-button">
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/per_christian_berg/" target="_blank" class="flex justify-center">
                  {{> icons/instagram class="h-6 w-6" }}
                  <span class="ml-2">Instagram</span>
                </a>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </main>
      {{> footer }}
    </div>
    {{> menu }}
  </body>
</html>
